{"tid":2142331,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"厲害了我的戰狼 劉曉明：支那冇錯 錯的是全世界","createTime":"2020-08-06T10:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T10:53:28.000Z","uid":242537,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bbae8c33fba5cf1fbecfa1450f27c1031fa57019","tid":2142331,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T10:43:23.000Z","msg":"中國駐英國大使劉曉明接受央視訪問，被問及中英關係的「黃金時代」是否已經結束，劉曉明指，中英關係面臨現在的困難，責任完全在英國一方。<br />\n<br />\n劉曉明表示，中方從來沒有干涉英國內政，但英方無端指責《香港國安法》，採取措施停止與香港的引渡協議，改變英國BNO護照持有人的地位，對香港禁運所謂的武器，而且對香港推遲立法會選舉說三道四，違反國際協議。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外劉曉明更指責英國內部某些官員挑起所謂的「中國威脅論」，惡化中英雙方的關係，讓英國在中英關係上的定位發生改變。"},{"pid":"ecc9990dd717f9bab96e191722e37d6f56700a53","tid":2142331,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T10:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fYUaoaP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfYUaoaP.jpg&h=a4ee10e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bceb4c31583481c3b4a20de7d9a83c3b0763d41","tid":2142331,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T10:44:28.000Z","msg":"武器都有得所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924ff7710292560f6c303d368c337fbc2e8cae02","tid":2142331,"uid":177590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T10:45:41.000Z","msg":"係無變<br />\n不嬲都咁衰"},{"pid":"2fbbe18f158235064bdeaf868108796947cecc73","tid":2142331,"uid":183758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T10:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xnrv7Dk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXnrv7Dk.gif&h=861dc6a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0846e58e5c0426dcbab2b9c319cb4b5cba0e67f","tid":2142331,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T10:51:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FENgjSWL.gif&amp;h=6a8ebc7a&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"cebb6d9c89bd8e6